+
+  /**
+   * Set the bottom slot, ie the "weakest" (sorted last)
+   * entry in the queue.  When {@link #compareBottom} is
+   * called, you should compare against this slot.  This
+   * will always be called before {@link #compareBottom}.
+   * 
